OL,7,FA group of families and individuals,
OL,8,Fwho are lobbying for a change of
OL,9,Fculture in Guernsey healthcare, have
OL,10,Fpulled out of a meeting with officials
OL,11,Fthis month following the arrest of the
OL,12,Fpolitician representing them.
OL,14,F'Families for Culture Change' has been
OL,15,Fsupported by Deputy Gavin St Pier to
OL,16,Fshare their stories, with him calling
OL,17,Ffor an independent inquiry into their
OL,18,Fconcerns.
