OL,7,FMore than 30 families have now reached
OL,8,Fout to Deputy St Pier, with a variety
OL,9,Fof complaints relating to healthcare,
OL,10,Fboth at the Medical Specialist Group
OL,11,Fand more generally under Health and
OL,12,FSocial Care.
OL,14,FIn representing them, Deputy St Pier
OL,15,Fhimself has attracted several Code of
OL,16,FConduct complaints - most recently
OL,17,Flate last year, when a complaint
OL,18,Flodged by a local paediatrician led to
OL,19,Fa lengthy debate in the States.
