OL,7,FDeputies were asked whether to suspend
OL,8,Fthe Deputy Chief Minister without pay
OL,9,Ffollowing a report by the States'
OL,10,Findependent Commissioner of Standards,
OL,11,Fwhich found him guilty of breaking the
OL,12,FCode by speaking to a Guardian
OL,13,Freporter about the families' concerns.
OL,15,FHis colleagues dismissed the report,
OL,16,Fleading to the Commissioner's
OL,17,Fresignation.
