OL,7,FThe President of Health and Social
OL,8,FCare, Dr George Oswald, subsequently
OL,9,Fannounced that work is underway to
OL,10,Fbroker a plan of reconciliation
OL,11,Fbetween the families and local
OL,12,Fhealthcare.
OL,14,FHowever, Deputy St Pier and his wife
OL,15,Fhave since been arrested following a
OL,16,Fcomplaint of harassment, leading to
OL,17,Fthe families pulling out of a
OL,18,Fpresentation to politicians set for
OL,19,Fthis month.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/12
