OL,7,FDeputy St Pier and his wife were both
OL,8,Freleased without charge, but the
OL,9,Ffamilies say it leaves them concerned
OL,10,Fabout reprisals if they speak out
OL,11,Fabout their experiences.
OL,13,FIn an email to all Guernsey Deputies,
OL,14,Fthey explained:
OL,16,FDear Deputies,
OL,18,FWe write to let you know that we are
OL,19,Fsadly no longer able to proceed with a
OL,20,Fpresentation to States members in
OL,21,FJanuary 2026.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/12
