OL,4,C'terrified' of speaking out after
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,FFor a very brief period after the Code
OL,8,Fof Conduct debate, we felt that our
OL,9,Fvoices might finally be heard.
OL,10,FHowever, the weaponisation of another
OL,11,Festablished system has been successful
OL,12,Fin silencing us again. This is a great
OL,13,Fshame and we can only hope that
OL,14,Fchanges will be made in future to
OL,15,Fensure that people who speak up can do
OL,16,Fso safely and without fear of reprisal.
OL,18,FKind regards,
OL,20,FFamilies for Culture Change
