OL,7,FITV News put these concerns to Health
OL,8,Fand Social Care, who did not want to
OL,9,Fcomment specifically on the group
OL,10,Fpulling out of the presentation.
OL,12,FInstead, it referred back to comments
OL,13,Fmade in relation to a series of
OL,14,Fquestions submitted by Deputy St Pier,
OL,15,Fwhere Deputy Oswald said a listening
OL,16,Fexercise has been launched with the
OL,17,Fsupport of Carewatch (an independent
OL,18,Fhealthcare oversight panel) into the
OL,19,Fconcerns of the families, and another
OL,20,Flistening exercise has been launched
OL,21,Fwith medical practitioners.
