OL,7,FThis working group is then expected to
OL,8,Fprovide recommendations about how to
OL,9,Fimprove the complaints process at a
OL,10,Flater date.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, the Medical Specialist
OL,13,FGroup has previously stated: "We take
OL,14,Fall concerns raised by patients and
OL,15,Ffamilies seriously, and we are
OL,16,Fcommitted to learning from every
OL,17,Fexperience to improve the care we
OL,18,Fprovide.
