OL,7,F"We welcome any opportunity to
OL,8,Fdemonstrate our commitment to
OL,9,Ftransparency and accountability in
OL,10,Fserving our patients."
OL,12,FITV News has learned that 339
OL,13,Fcomplaints were made about healthcare
OL,14,Fin Guernsey in the last three years,
OL,15,Fwhich averages to around two per week.
